---
import Layout from '../layouts/BarringtonLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Barrington Mobile Tire Pros" description="Learn about Barrington Mobile Tire Pros. Serving Barrington, IL and NW suburbs for over 10 years with reliable mobile tire installation and repair services.">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-12 md:pt-40 md:pb-20 bg-surface-light">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-brand-dark mb-6 tracking-tight">About Barrington <br class="hidden md:block" /> Mobile Tire Pros.</h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-500 max-w-3xl font-light leading-relaxed">Your local experts in mobile tire service. <br class="hidden md:block" /> Serving Barrington and surrounding NW suburbs.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-barrington-primary mb-6">Serving Barrington & NW Suburbs for 10+ Years</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                At Barrington Mobile Tire Pros, we believe that getting new tires shouldn't be a hassle. For over a decade, we've been serving the Barrington community with a simple mission: <strong>bring the tire shop to the customer.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-12 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                We understand that your time is valuable. Whether you're a busy professional working from home, a parent juggling school runs, or managing a fleet of vehicles, waiting at a tire shop is the last thing you want to do. That's why we invested in state-of-the-art mobile tire vans equipped with the latest mounting and balancing technology.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-barrington-primary mb-6">Why Choose Us?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-12">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">check_circle</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong class="block text-slate-900">Convenience</strong>
                        <span class="text-slate-600">We come to your home, office, or roadside location.</span>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">check_circle</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong class="block text-slate-900">Expertise</strong>
                        <span class="text-slate-600">Our technicians are TIA-certified and experienced with all vehicle types, from sedans to luxury SUVs.</span>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">check_circle</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong class="block text-slate-900">Fair Pricing</strong>
                        <span class="text-slate-600">We operate with lower overhead than traditional shops, passing the savings on to you.</span>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">check_circle</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong class="block text-slate-900">Safety</strong>
                        <span class="text-slate-600">We use precision balancing and torque specifications to ensure your safety on the road.</span>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <div class="text-center">
                <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition-all duration-200 bg-brand-dark rounded-full hover:bg-brand-light hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/20 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Contact Us Today
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
